            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I have some misunderstands on TUI. And I found a documentation from rxvt which describes some escape sequences:\r\n[xterm commands](http://pod.tst.eu/http://cvs.schmorp.de/rxvt-unicode/doc/rxvt.7.pod#XTerm_Operating_System_Commands)\r\n#16592 fixed this issue with Ps = 11, There is also an escape sequence to change the color of the terminal border when Ps = 708. I've tested it on kitty/alacritty and urxvt. Only urxvt will treat background and border differently.",
