            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "This issue happened when users where customizing their scheme and opting-in for `termguicolors`.\r\n\r\nBut now that the default scheme is redefining the background color and setting `termguicolors` when available (#26334, #26407), maybe we should consider sending this control sequence by default after loading themes?\r\n\r\nOtherwise, users updating from a default scheme and background setup are likely to see this padding.",
